<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Support Chat Summary</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: auto;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .chat-container {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            max-height: 300px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .message {
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .user {
            background: #e5e5e5;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .support {
            background: #ffd251;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            margin-top: 0px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .logo {
            height: 60px;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;

        }

        .logo img {
            height: 100%;
            width: 60px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://tiptop-stag.syd1.digitaloceanspaces.com/staging/TiptopUser.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <p>Dear {{NAME}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for reaching out to our support team. Below is a summary of your conversation:</p>
        <div class="chat-container">
            {{#each DATA}}
            {{#if receiver_type}}
            <div class="message support"><strong>{{sender}}:</strong> {{message}}</div>
            {{else}}
            <div class="message user"><strong>{{sender}}:</strong> {{message}}</div>
            {{/if}}
            {{/each}}
            <!-- Add more messages dynamically -->
        </div>
        <p>If you have any further questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
        <div class="footer" style="margin-top: 50px;">
            <p>Regards,</p>
            <p>TipTop Ride (TipTop Transport Solutions)</p>
            <p>Quality, Trusted & Professional.</p>
            <p>Branch and Base: Mascot, Sydney, NSW, Australia.</p>
            <p>24/7 Contact Numbers : 02 96699390 (LOCALS), +61296699390 (INTERNATIONAL)</p>
            <p>TipTop Transport Solutions PTY LTD Â© All Rights Reserved.2025</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>